Package: redis
Architecture: any
Depends:
 redis-server (= ${binary:Version}),
 redis-module-search (= ${binary:Version}) [amd64 arm64],
 redis-module-json (= ${binary:Version}) [amd64 arm64],
 redis-module-bloom (= ${binary:Version}) [amd64 arm64],
 redis-module-timeseries (= ${binary:Version}) [amd64 arm64],
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: Persistent key-value database with network interface (metapackage)
 Redis is a key-value database in a similar vein to memcache but the dataset
 is non-volatile. Redis additionally provides native support for atomically
 manipulating and querying data structures such as lists and sets.
 .
 The dataset is stored entirely in memory and periodically flushed to disk.
 .
 This package depends on the redis-server package and all core Redis modules
 (RediSearch, RedisJSON, RedisBloom, RedisTimeSeries) on supported architectures.

