Package: redis-module-search
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends:
 redis-server (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: RediSearch module for Redis
 RediSearch is a Redis module that provides querying, secondary indexing, and
 full-text search for Redis. These features enable multi-field queries,
 aggregation, exact phrase matching, and numeric filtering for text queries.
 .
 This package contains the RediSearch module for Redis.

Package: redis-module-json
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends:
 redis-server (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: RedisJSON module for Redis
 RedisJSON is a Redis module that implements ECMA-404 The JSON Data Interchange
 Standard as a native data type. It allows storing, updating and fetching JSON
 values from Redis keys (documents).
 .
 This package contains the RedisJSON module for Redis.

Package: redis-module-bloom
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends:
 redis-server (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: RedisBloom module for Redis
 RedisBloom is a Redis module that provides probabilistic data structures for
 Redis. These include Bloom Filter, Cuckoo Filter, Count-Min-Sketch, and
 Top-K data structures.
 .
 This package contains the RedisBloom module for Redis.

Package: redis-module-timeseries
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends:
 redis-server (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: RedisTimeSeries module for Redis
 RedisTimeSeries is a Redis module that adds a time series data structure to
 Redis. It provides high performance ingestion and low latency queries for
 time series data.
 .
 This package contains the RedisTimeSeries module for Redis.
